primary: {
  type: "install"
  message: <<EOM
USAGE:

To enable monit on *BSD you need to add monit_enable="YES" to rc.conf file.
To enable monit on a SunOS system, use "svcadm enable monit" command.

Before running monit you may have to modify the provided monitrc
configuration file located at %%PREFIX%%/etc/monitrc
EOM
}
